title: 1221 Johnathan Haidt
description:
Johnathan Haidt is a college professor and author. He talks to Joe about how best to raise kids and the problem with the way parents are raising kids today. He and joe have a great conversation and there’s really a lot to learn in it if you’re a new parent or thinking of having children. Definitely worth a listen.
